<!-- WHO WE ARE -->
<section>
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="who-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Who We Are</div>
        <h2 class="serif-h who-h">MPL Pursuits was built for the players who want <em>more.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="body-copy">We are dedicated to helping tennis players of all levels reach their fullest potential — on the court, in competition, and in their personal development. Designed with both players and parents in mind, our mission is to provide clear instruction, structured development pathways, and the essential knowledge needed to succeed in the ever-evolving world of tennis.</p>
        <p class="body-copy" style="margin-top:1.25rem">We believe that when athletes and families are educated, supported, and aligned, real progress begins. We equip players with the skills, confidence, and strategic understanding required to perform consistently at their best.</p>
        <p class="body-copy" style="margin-top:1.25rem">Through private virtual coaching and detailed online video analysis, athletes receive personalized feedback that accelerates growth and helps them master the technical and tactical aspects of their game.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><i class="ti ti-video" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="service-title">Virtual Private Coaching</div><p class="body-copy">Personalized sessions tailored to your game</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><i class="ti ti-chart-bar" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="service-title">Online Video Analysis</div><p class="body-copy">Detailed technical feedback from elite coaches</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><i class="ti ti-brain" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="service-title">Mental Performance Training</div><p class="body-copy">Sports psychology applied to match play</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><i class="ti ti-school" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="service-title">College Recruiting Guidance</div><p class="body-copy">End-to-end roadmap for college-bound athletes</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
<section>
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">Our Philosophy</div>
    <h2 class="serif-h" style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:2.5rem">We Coach the Whole Athlete.<br>Not Just the <em>Forehand.</em></h2>
    <div class="phil-grid">
      <div class="phil-card"><div class="phil-num">01</div><div class="phil-title">Holistic Player Development</div><p class="body-copy">We believe in coaching the whole athlete — technically, mentally, physically, and emotionally. True tennis performance comes not just from clean strokes, but from disciplined habits, strong footwork, intentional preparation, and strategic thinking.</p></div>
      <div class="phil-card"><div class="phil-num">02</div><div class="phil-title">Progress Over Perfection</div><p class="body-copy">We emphasize growth as a continuous journey. Every drill, practice session, and match is an opportunity to improve. We encourage athletes to embrace challenges, reflect honestly on their development, and transform setbacks into lessons.</p></div>
      <div class="phil-card"><div class="phil-num">03</div><div class="phil-title">Education for Players and Parents</div><p class="body-copy">Tennis requires thoughtful planning and informed decision-making. We provide families with clear guidance on training structure, tournament selection, mental preparation, recovery routines, and long-term pathways including college tennis opportunities.</p></div>
      <div class="phil-card"><div class="phil-num">04</div><div class="phil-title">Character Through Competition</div><p class="body-copy">We use tennis as a platform to cultivate character. Pressure reveals strengths and areas for growth. We help athletes develop resilience, sportsmanship, confidence, and self-leadership — qualities that carry into every part of their lives.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

